public interface IFlowAnalysis<LE>

All flow analyses must be able to return the information defined by this interface.

Method Detail

getResultsBefore

LE getResultsBefore(org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTNode node)
Retrieves the analysis state that exists before analyzing the node. Before is respective to normal program flow and not the direction of the analysis.

Parameters:
node - the ASTNode of interest
Returns:
the lattice that represents the analysis state before analyzing the node. Or null if the node doesn't have a corresponding control flow node.
